name: Finn Jarpane
content:
Finn Jarpane was a Human female gambler who was affiliated with the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the Galactic Civil War against the Galactic Empire. Jarpane was skilled at dodging, bargaining, gambling, and use of blasters and starship weaponry. She was also culturally knowledgeable and stood 1.7 meters. She carried a hold-out blaster, a medpac, and a sabacc deck, and wore a tunic, pants, boots, and a belt.
Finn Jarpane was created for the Rebel Characters Adventure Set, a boxed set of metal miniatures released in 1989 by West End Games to be used with Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. Jarpane's character type was listed as "Female Gambler" and her model came unpainted.
